### Create Project
POST http://localhost:4004/admin/Projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "HR Management System",
  "description": "Employee and Department Management Project",
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-12-31",
  "budget": 500000,
  "status": "Active"
}
### Assign Employee to Project
POST http://localhost:4004/admin/Assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Developer",
  "allocation": 100,
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-12-31",
  "employee_ID": "PUT_EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE",
  "project_ID": "PUT_PROJECT_ID_HERE"
}

